{"tid":1301810,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【713 光復上水UPDATE】","createTime":"2019-07-09T17:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T07:40:41.000Z","uid":37516,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"03f9f0bd8dbfbefb2d7f1919042ce51d6556891b","tid":1301810,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCwbXU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCwbXU4.png&h=25ea9613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚我們同接近20位警方人員係上水警署開會商討遊行路線及安排，由於警方評估後認為今次遊行將會有大量人參與，而原集合地點 &ndash; 「上水花園第一號」無法容納參與遊行的人士，故此建議我們將遊行集合地點改為面積更大的 -「北區運動場籃球場」，以便容納更加多的參與人士。<br />\n<br />\n在跟警方商討後，我們決定接納警方的建議，將集合地點改為「北區運動場籃球場」，敬請各位留意。<br />\n<br />\n「不反對通知書」仍在批核階段，相信我們於短期內會收到警方就是次遊行發出的「不反對通知書」。如有進一步的消息，我們會盡快向各位公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消息發佈:<br />\n請留意本專頁 或<br />\nTelegram Channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Assemble713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAssemble713&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=9366ce7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Assemble713</a><br />\n<br />\n招募義工:<br />\n由於警方要求我們安排糾察或義工沿途維持秩序，如有意成為義工，請經INBOX聯絡我們  或<br />\n加入Telegram 群組:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LkY6chN10ReoCdIwHIq9ug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLkY6chN10ReoCdIwHIq9ug&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBLPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=6eaff15f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LkY6chN10ReoCdIwHIq9ug</a>"},{"pid":"9d30869d9f21cfff2f6b49f7f830e7c4a9ee4bec","tid":1301810,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:47:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff613feb19d942de643b3b7130e4f569a43530fc","tid":1301810,"uid":259415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:49:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11ef02e17d582bcf86086f5ad81c7135c88be45","tid":1301810,"uid":265535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:49:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b89d7496cbbf19df083c1e8a7441c34aef2e80d6","tid":1301810,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:01:02.000Z","msg":"歡迎入嚟一齊討論啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「長文慎入」勇武又好、和理非又好，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"56ef8a3664839f0cab3bca0f6a39c1e489077321","tid":1301810,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:08:22.000Z","msg":"屌班狗真係麻撚煩。<br />\n到時帶memo隨行隨貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc5d08061bdda9b963e1c14eaa6a7d669a3be22","tid":1301810,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T00:48:52.000Z","msg":"推， 好似冇乜人講咁"},{"pid":"0329a0cb2cb38db645249d0bbcbd3f481c84f455","tid":1301810,"uid":274569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e89514f970d8babcf51125895b1b9d5e8dec325","tid":1301810,"uid":240869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:07:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1f5dab06cbeb3fa7b5804b6f9498491d9557f28","tid":1301810,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"目前戰線太多，運動重心稍為偏離；大家花太多時間係寶礦力同連儂場上面。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地需要集中火力係五大訴求上面。</span></span></strong>只有個議題仲係度，個運動先繼續有力量做其他野。重心要放返係「送中」上面，連帶反黑警；連儂場唔好太執著、反TVB唔好反多過林鄭。先搞「送中」，燈柱同信用評分先慢慢普及。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重心一定要放返係「送中」上面！<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聚焦五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連儂牆由得佢，第日再整過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><